  "general_provisions": "This bill amends provisions related to food safety and sanitation for child care providers.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>exempts child care food preparation kitchens from food service establishment regulations under certain circumstances;<hr><ltbullet>requires the Department of Health and Human Services, in collaboration with child care provider associations, to make rules for child care food preparation kitchens:<hr><ltbullet1>for food safety and sanitation; and<hr><ltbullet1>to qualify for certain exemptions; and<hr><ltbullet>defines terms.",
